WEBVTT

01:50.720 --> 01:51.360
Yuanbao.

01:52.000 --> 01:52.920
Keep acting.

01:53.000 --> 01:53.880
Keep acting.

01:53.960 --> 01:54.680
Come on.

01:54.880 --> 01:55.920
I am here.

02:34.000 --> 02:35.720
It seems I shouldn't have come here.

02:35.720 --> 02:37.980
It's too late for you to realize that now.

02:39.440 --> 02:41.300
Can I leave some memories behind?

02:41.320 --> 02:43.000
I don't want to leave any memories.

02:43.000 --> 02:45.079
If you want to leave something, leave yourself.

02:45.079 --> 02:46.440
You can only get my body.

02:46.840 --> 02:48.100
You won't get my heart.

02:49.800 --> 02:51.060
We won't have a future.

02:51.160 --> 02:52.040
Just let me go.

02:52.320 --> 02:54.440
Fine, I can let you go.

02:55.360 --> 02:57.720
But you must hug me before you go.

02:58.920 --> 03:00.800
I am a sunset warrior after all.

03:01.280 --> 03:03.280
If I hug you just because you ask me to.

03:03.280 --> 03:04.480
Where is my pride?

03:05.040 --> 03:05.920
You're lying.

03:06.480 --> 03:07.810
You don't dare to hug me.

03:07.880 --> 03:10.280
Which means you still have feelings for me.

03:10.440 --> 03:11.440
Let me tell you.

03:12.040 --> 03:13.840
If you reject me today.

03:14.080 --> 03:15.520
You'll regret it for the rest of your life.

03:15.520 --> 03:17.120
I won't hug you even if I regret it.

03:17.120 --> 03:20.800
We can only blame destiny.

03:48.520 --> 03:49.760
It's been 18 years.

03:50.360 --> 03:51.520
It seems like this is the first time

03:51.520 --> 03:53.840
I've looked into his eyes so closely.

03:54.520 --> 03:58.320
At this moment, his eyes seem to hold the sea of stars.

04:02.120 --> 04:03.920
Qingyun is so handsome.

04:04.520 --> 04:07.440
I didn't know Qingyun was such a good actor.

04:27.960 --> 04:28.920
Watch out!

04:37.720 --> 04:38.320
Yuanbao.

04:38.640 --> 04:39.920
Yuanbao.

04:40.000 --> 04:42.040
Yuanbao.

04:42.120 --> 04:43.640
What's wrong? Are you okay?

04:43.640 --> 04:45.100
Hurry, call an ambulance!

04:45.680 --> 04:46.480
Make the call!

04:47.120 --> 04:47.800
Hurry!

04:47.840 --> 04:48.600
Come on.

04:48.680 --> 04:49.440
Be careful.

04:50.440 --> 04:51.200
Slow down.

04:51.240 --> 04:52.000
Yuanbao, don't be afraid.

04:52.000 --> 04:53.159
We are going to the hospital right now.

04:53.159 --> 04:54.159
Tell the teacher. Hurry!

04:54.159 --> 04:54.560
Okay.

04:54.560 --> 04:56.020
Hurry, call an ambulance!

04:56.680 --> 04:57.560
Slow down.

04:58.440 --> 04:59.120
Slow down.

04:59.159 --> 05:00.520
Slow down.

05:18.240 --> 05:19.120
Yuanbao.

05:19.560 --> 05:20.240
Grandma.

05:20.640 --> 05:22.360
Doctor, how is she?

05:22.520 --> 05:23.580
How is it, Yuanbao?

05:23.720 --> 05:25.720
Don't worry, we've checked everything.

05:25.720 --> 05:27.120
Fortunately,

05:27.160 --> 05:28.440
her eyeball was not injured.

05:28.440 --> 05:29.800
Her brow bone and upper eyelid

05:29.800 --> 05:31.320
were scratched by broken glass,

05:31.320 --> 05:32.520
which is why she bled.

05:32.560 --> 05:34.080
However, considering she is a girl,

05:34.080 --> 05:35.610
we didn't give her stitches

05:35.760 --> 05:36.800
for fear of leaving scars.

05:36.800 --> 05:38.120
But we have treated her wound,

05:38.120 --> 05:39.240
and it will heal properly.

05:39.240 --> 05:40.200
But remember,

05:40.320 --> 05:42.440
you must come to change the dressing every two days.

05:42.440 --> 05:44.800
Most importantly, don't make big movements.

05:44.800 --> 05:46.840
Otherwise, the wound won't heal well.

05:46.840 --> 05:49.600
Doctor, it definitely won't leave a scar, right?

05:49.760 --> 05:51.720
It's hard to say.

05:51.840 --> 05:53.480
It depends on how you recover.

05:53.480 --> 05:54.840
But we already have

05:54.920 --> 05:56.560
scar removal technology.

05:56.880 --> 05:58.680
Even if a little scar remains,

05:58.800 --> 06:00.840
it can be treated with technology.

06:01.320 --> 06:04.920
Doctor, can I take this gauze off first?

06:05.240 --> 06:07.570
I have an important performance tonight.

06:07.600 --> 06:08.920
After my competition is over,

06:08.920 --> 06:11.320
can I put this gauze back on?

06:11.520 --> 06:12.040
Well,

06:12.080 --> 06:14.000
why are you still thinking about the performance?

06:14.000 --> 06:15.200
If it weren't for this performance,

06:15.200 --> 06:17.000
would your eye have gotten hurt?

06:17.240 --> 06:18.120
That won't do.

06:18.240 --> 06:20.320
If you take it off now, the wound will tear,

06:20.320 --> 06:21.400
and it will get infected.

06:21.400 --> 06:23.520
You should also try not to make big movements

06:23.520 --> 06:25.720
or facial expressions around the eyes.

06:25.720 --> 06:26.680
Yuanbao's mom,

06:27.320 --> 06:28.440
I'm really sorry.

06:28.720 --> 06:30.440
The child was injured at school.

06:30.440 --> 06:31.770
We really didn't expect

06:31.880 --> 06:33.960
that there would be a problem with the school auditorium lights.

06:33.960 --> 06:35.640
The school will cover the medical expenses.

06:35.640 --> 06:36.640
I'm really sorry.

06:36.760 --> 06:39.120
Mr. Tian, we can't blame you.

06:39.400 --> 06:40.720
This was just an accident.

06:40.720 --> 06:41.480
Thank you.

06:41.680 --> 06:43.340
Thank you for understanding.

06:43.960 --> 06:45.400
I'll go prescribe the medicine first.

06:45.400 --> 06:46.480
Family members, please remember

06:46.480 --> 06:48.520
to come and pick up the medicine with the prescription later.

06:48.520 --> 06:50.400
Okay. Thank you, doctor.

06:51.640 --> 06:53.520
Mom. Grandma.

06:54.040 --> 06:55.240
Listen to the doctor.

06:55.360 --> 06:57.560
Fortunately, your eyes weren't injured.

06:57.560 --> 06:58.920
Don't think about anything right now.

06:58.920 --> 07:01.360
Recovering your eyes is the most important thing.

07:01.360 --> 07:03.640
Mr. Tian, Yuanbao...

07:04.000 --> 07:05.000
I understand.

07:05.240 --> 07:06.570
Her health comes first.

07:07.640 --> 07:10.240
Yuanbao, just focus on recovering now.

07:10.440 --> 07:12.760
Don't worry about the class competition.

07:12.760 --> 07:14.520
The classes you miss these days,

07:14.520 --> 07:16.440
I will ask the teachers to help you catch up.

07:16.440 --> 07:17.480
Get well soon.

07:17.960 --> 07:20.440
Mr. Tian, about tonight's performance,

07:20.520 --> 07:21.840
how are you going to arrange it?

07:21.840 --> 07:23.500
I called Meng Jingu's family.

07:24.200 --> 07:25.400
He has some family issues.

07:25.400 --> 07:27.000
Now you are injured too.

07:27.440 --> 07:29.840
We have to withdraw from this competition.

07:29.920 --> 07:32.120
It's fine. There will be other chances.

07:32.360 --> 07:33.760
This drama competition,

07:33.960 --> 07:35.200
our whole class

07:35.280 --> 07:37.480
has prepared carefully for a long time.

07:37.840 --> 07:39.440
It's tonight.

07:39.680 --> 07:40.800
If because of me,

07:40.880 --> 07:42.800
causing everyone to quit the competition,

07:42.800 --> 07:44.640
I would really be to blame.

07:45.320 --> 07:46.780
I understand how you feel.

07:47.080 --> 07:48.740
But there is nothing we can do.

07:49.680 --> 07:50.440
Mutou.

07:52.120 --> 07:53.320
Can you and Xing Yaqi

07:53.760 --> 07:55.800
perform on stage instead of us?

07:56.720 --> 07:58.000
I don't want to go.

07:58.240 --> 07:59.840
I want to stay and take care of you.

07:59.840 --> 08:01.640
Didn't the doctor say I'm fine?

08:02.120 --> 08:04.480
Besides, the scenes of Joker and Zixia

08:04.600 --> 08:06.730
only you and Xing Yaqi have practiced.

08:07.120 --> 08:08.320
Now that Meng Jingu and I

08:08.320 --> 08:09.720
both can't participate.

08:09.880 --> 08:11.240
How can we bear

08:11.280 --> 08:13.800
to see our classmates' efforts go to waste?

08:14.400 --> 08:16.560
Just consider it as me begging you, okay?

08:16.560 --> 08:17.280
Go.

08:17.680 --> 08:18.760
That's a way.

08:19.960 --> 08:22.220
Mu Qingyun, why don't you think about it?

08:22.440 --> 08:23.840
Didn't you tell me before

08:24.000 --> 08:25.460
that you want to act again?

08:26.000 --> 08:28.460
You told the teacher you wanted to act again.

08:29.320 --> 08:32.039
Qingyun, since this is about the class,

08:32.120 --> 08:33.720
you should help if you can.

08:33.919 --> 08:34.960
This way you can also

08:34.960 --> 08:37.159
let Yuanbao recover with peace of mind.

08:41.880 --> 08:43.039
There is one thing

08:46.040 --> 08:47.320
I want to ask of you.

08:50.520 --> 08:51.240
Tell me.

08:51.720 --> 08:53.040
Can I go take a look?

08:53.480 --> 08:55.480
You still want to go in this condition?

08:55.480 --> 08:56.400
Can I?

08:58.120 --> 09:00.160
Well, since they want to go so badly,

09:00.640 --> 09:02.160
let's go with them.

09:03.680 --> 09:05.040
I really don't know what to do with you.

09:05.040 --> 09:07.200
Let's go.

09:20.000 --> 09:21.330
Have you figured it out?

09:22.680 --> 09:23.810
Where are you going?

09:24.720 --> 09:25.480
Jingu.

09:27.520 --> 09:28.400
This kid.

09:28.720 --> 09:29.600
Zhi Zun Bao.

09:31.120 --> 09:32.680
Don't talk this nonsense to me.

09:32.680 --> 09:34.610
I said you've got the wrong person.

09:35.360 --> 09:36.620
This Purple Gold Bell,

09:36.840 --> 09:38.040
how do you explain it?

09:39.280 --> 09:41.840
Zhi Zun Bao, prepare to die!

09:54.000 --> 09:56.200
Great Sage Equal to Heaven, Sun Wukong.

09:57.120 --> 09:58.400
I am Zixia.

10:00.680 --> 10:03.840
My true love is a peerless hero.

10:05.000 --> 10:09.360
One day, he will wear golden armor

10:10.240 --> 10:12.770
and ride on seven-colored clouds to marry me.

10:13.480 --> 10:15.120
I guessed the beginning,

10:16.400 --> 10:18.440
but I couldn't guess the ending.

10:26.280 --> 10:27.480
Zixia.

10:57.200 --> 10:58.040
Okay.

11:05.840 --> 11:06.040
Go up, Yuanbao.

11:06.040 --> 11:06.440
Go up, Yuanbao.

11:06.440 --> 11:07.300
Go up, Yuanbao.

11:08.840 --> 11:09.560
Let's go.

11:13.560 --> 11:15.480
Yuanbao, let's go up together.

11:15.600 --> 11:17.240
You must be careful.

11:17.240 --> 11:17.640
Let's go.

11:17.640 --> 11:19.000
Take good care of her.

11:25.920 --> 11:26.680
Yuanbao.

11:26.720 --> 11:28.600
Yuanbao.

11:28.760 --> 11:29.690
You are awesome.

11:41.720 --> 11:43.600
Come on, let's take a bow together.

11:43.600 --> 11:44.320
Okay.

11:57.800 --> 11:59.160
Yuanbao.

12:05.040 --> 12:05.840
What's wrong?

12:05.920 --> 12:06.980
Yuanbao! Yuanbao!

12:25.360 --> 12:26.420
Yuanbao, don't go.

12:43.840 --> 12:45.280
Yuanbao, you're awake.

12:46.000 --> 12:47.080
Yuanbao is awake.

12:48.400 --> 12:49.530
How are you feeling?

12:50.040 --> 12:51.560
Why am I at home?

12:52.080 --> 12:54.140
Where else would you be if not at home?

12:54.760 --> 12:55.840
Yuanbao.

12:56.240 --> 12:57.440
You're awake.

12:57.720 --> 12:58.920
Do your eyes still hurt?

12:58.920 --> 13:00.960
Yuanbao, are you still dizzy?

13:01.120 --> 13:02.200
I'm fine.

13:02.720 --> 13:04.400
Since when have I been here?

13:04.880 --> 13:06.560
Wasn't I in the auditorium?

13:06.680 --> 13:07.560
Don't even mention it.

13:07.560 --> 13:08.920
You scared us to death.

13:09.160 --> 13:09.560
Yeah.

13:09.560 --> 13:12.000
The doctor said you've been too tired lately,

13:12.000 --> 13:13.720
and you didn't eat anything all day,

13:13.720 --> 13:15.180
so you had low blood sugar.

13:15.320 --> 13:17.200
You passed out in the auditorium.

13:17.680 --> 13:19.760
Here, drink some brown sugar water.

13:20.120 --> 13:20.400
Here.

13:20.400 --> 13:21.530
I'll do it, Grandma.

13:21.640 --> 13:23.170
Blow on it for her. It's hot.

13:26.760 --> 13:27.560
Drink slowly.

13:28.200 --> 13:29.600
Drink more brown sugar water.

13:29.600 --> 13:30.400
Drink up.

13:32.080 --> 13:34.160
After dinner, have some fruit.

13:34.360 --> 13:36.490
We need to keep up with your nutrition.

13:40.840 --> 13:41.880
What time is it?

13:42.600 --> 13:44.200
It's past eleven.

13:44.360 --> 13:47.290
You've been sleeping since you came back yesterday.

13:52.760 --> 13:54.320
I slept so well.

13:54.920 --> 13:55.840
Grandma made you

13:55.840 --> 13:57.700
your favorite braised pork ribs.

13:57.840 --> 13:58.840
Get up quickly.

13:58.920 --> 14:00.720
Get up, wash up, and let's eat.

14:03.160 --> 14:04.090
Do you want some?

14:06.960 --> 14:08.680
You scared me. Get up.

14:11.360 --> 14:13.280
How are you? Are you feeling okay?

14:17.720 --> 14:19.400
Slow down, slow down, slow down.

14:19.400 --> 14:20.240
Slow down.

14:21.760 --> 14:22.440
Slow down.

14:22.600 --> 14:23.520
Come, sweetie.

14:23.840 --> 14:24.920
Drink some soup.

14:25.240 --> 14:26.840
It has medicinal herbs in it.

14:26.880 --> 14:28.480
It's specially for your eyes.

14:28.480 --> 14:29.360
Drink up.

14:33.400 --> 14:34.080
Good.

14:37.480 --> 14:38.520
By the way, Mutou.

14:38.880 --> 14:42.160
Thanks for agreeing to perform on stage.

14:42.840 --> 14:44.640
If it weren't for you,

14:45.240 --> 14:47.770
everyone's hard work would have been wasted.

14:48.200 --> 14:48.960
All right.

14:49.320 --> 14:50.880
Let bygones be bygones.

14:51.200 --> 14:51.920
From now on, you two

14:51.920 --> 14:54.050
must focus on your studies and behave.

14:54.200 --> 14:56.240
No more thinking about things other than studying.

14:56.240 --> 14:57.040
Do you hear me?

14:57.200 --> 14:57.960
Got it, Mom.

14:58.120 --> 14:58.880
I know.

15:08.200 --> 15:09.600
What are you laughing at?

15:09.640 --> 15:11.080
Try covering one eye.

15:11.600 --> 15:13.530
You'd definitely be worse than me.

15:13.880 --> 15:16.720
Having only one eye is so uncomfortable.

15:17.120 --> 15:18.380
I can't walk straight,

15:18.760 --> 15:20.200
can't pick up food,

15:20.520 --> 15:21.760
and I feel dizzy.

15:22.200 --> 15:24.530
Let's see if you'll join the fun next time.

15:25.120 --> 15:27.360
You're never this active when it comes to studying.

15:27.360 --> 15:28.560
But for other things,

15:28.560 --> 15:30.490
you're always the first to rush in.

15:31.240 --> 15:32.600
This is a lesson for you.

15:33.240 --> 15:36.640
Grandma, I'm the victim here too, okay?

15:37.080 --> 15:38.740
The light exploded suddenly.

15:38.840 --> 15:40.700
I couldn't have seen that coming.

15:40.800 --> 15:42.760
It's really not my fault this time.

15:42.960 --> 15:44.090
What is this called?

15:44.200 --> 15:46.400
It's an unexpected disaster.

15:48.640 --> 15:49.320
Grandma.

15:50.000 --> 15:51.120
Actually,

15:51.760 --> 15:54.220
Yuanbao got hurt trying to save me this time.

15:54.880 --> 15:55.800
Really?

15:57.680 --> 15:59.360
If Yuanbao hadn't pushed me,

16:00.240 --> 16:02.080
I would be the one injured now.

16:03.920 --> 16:05.840
Don't listen to his nonsense.

16:06.320 --> 16:07.040
I,

16:07.600 --> 16:10.800
I just pushed him subconsciously.

16:11.160 --> 16:12.840
I'm not as great as he says.

16:13.000 --> 16:14.400
Don't flatter yourself.

16:14.960 --> 16:15.720
Alright,

16:16.320 --> 16:17.920
it was Yuanbao who saved you.

16:18.040 --> 16:20.440
Exactly. We're a family.

16:20.520 --> 16:21.650
Don't be a stranger.

16:22.600 --> 16:24.160
Qingyun, come, eat.

16:24.440 --> 16:25.440
Thank you, Grandma.

16:25.440 --> 16:26.080
By the way,

16:27.160 --> 16:28.760
your eye is injured,

16:28.840 --> 16:30.840
what about your missed schoolwork?

16:31.600 --> 16:32.400
Qingyun.

16:33.920 --> 16:34.520
Forget it.

16:35.160 --> 16:37.620
You probably can't help her catch up either.

16:38.440 --> 16:40.280
What's the name of your desk mate?

16:40.280 --> 16:41.200
Something Jin.

16:41.400 --> 16:42.320
Meng Jingu.

16:43.280 --> 16:44.160
Right, right.

16:44.520 --> 16:46.080
Isn't he really good at studying?

16:46.080 --> 16:47.940
How about you ask him to tutor you?

16:50.200 --> 16:52.840
I already bother him too much.

16:53.320 --> 16:54.450
It's not a good idea.

16:54.640 --> 16:55.480
True,

16:55.800 --> 16:58.060
he probably doesn't have that much time.

16:59.120 --> 17:00.360
How about I try?

17:01.320 --> 17:02.480
Give me a break.

17:05.200 --> 17:06.599
What are you laughing at?

17:09.359 --> 17:12.290
Even if you dared to tutor me, I wouldn't dare listen.

17:12.520 --> 17:15.079
I'm afraid you'll drag me down to last place.

17:17.400 --> 17:18.530
That's ridiculous.

17:18.680 --> 17:20.210
Just because you said that,

17:20.280 --> 17:21.680
I have to tutor you.

17:22.400 --> 17:24.720
If I can memorize all the questions the teacher explains in class

17:24.720 --> 17:26.050
and explain them to you,

17:26.200 --> 17:28.660
how about you treat me to fried chicken legs?

17:29.640 --> 17:32.240
That's a good idea. Improve together.

17:32.400 --> 17:33.760
Then you'd better work hard.

17:33.760 --> 17:35.290
If you teach Yuanbao wrong,

17:35.400 --> 17:36.530
you'll be punished.

17:37.480 --> 17:38.040
Okay.

17:39.600 --> 17:41.400
It's a deal. Pinky promise.

17:41.760 --> 17:42.620
Pinky promise.

17:42.680 --> 17:43.720
Don't regret it.

17:44.040 --> 17:45.080
We'll see who regrets it.

17:45.080 --> 17:47.480
I'm definitely eating that fried chicken.

17:48.520 --> 17:50.080
Grandma and I are witnesses.

17:50.080 --> 17:51.600
Neither of you can back out.

17:51.600 --> 17:52.960
Hurry, eat.

17:53.200 --> 17:54.600
The food is getting cold.

18:03.480 --> 18:04.840
You didn't rest well at home,

18:04.840 --> 18:06.100
and sneaked out alone.

18:06.480 --> 18:08.240
Are you feeling sad

18:08.480 --> 18:09.720
because you couldn't perform on stage?

18:09.720 --> 18:11.120
Not exactly.

18:11.760 --> 18:12.820
Then what's wrong?

18:13.240 --> 18:14.120
Mutou,

18:14.840 --> 18:16.320
tell me honestly,

18:16.440 --> 18:17.600
am I

18:17.680 --> 18:19.480
a really annoying person?

18:22.160 --> 18:23.640
Why ask that suddenly?

18:24.080 --> 18:24.960
Nothing.

18:26.200 --> 18:28.240
I just feel that since Meng Jingu

18:28.280 --> 18:29.520
came to our class

18:30.200 --> 18:31.680
and became my desk mate,

18:32.200 --> 18:34.480
I seem to be always bothering him.

18:34.960 --> 18:36.800
I ask him questions I don't know,

18:37.200 --> 18:39.660
and ask him about homework I can't remember.

18:39.720 --> 18:41.800
I tried so hard, but in the end,

18:42.240 --> 18:43.480
I just kept

18:43.480 --> 18:44.880
holding others back.

18:50.240 --> 18:52.440
He's not as good as you say.

18:54.160 --> 18:56.020
And you're not as bad as you think.

18:57.120 --> 18:59.560
You've made great progress lately, you know?

18:59.560 --> 19:01.040
Your grades are improving,

19:01.040 --> 19:03.000
and your New Concept Essay was so good.

19:03.000 --> 19:05.040
I also know that to play Zixia,

19:05.200 --> 19:07.800
you stayed up half the night memorizing lines.

19:09.000 --> 19:12.260
How do you know I stayed up half the night memorizing lines?

19:12.640 --> 19:14.000
Grandma told me.

19:18.240 --> 19:19.760
Don't let one thing

19:19.840 --> 19:21.570
make you doubt yourself, okay?

19:21.640 --> 19:23.640
How can I not doubt myself?

19:25.560 --> 19:27.000
Do you know why Meng Jingu

19:27.080 --> 19:28.760
didn't show up in the end?

19:30.800 --> 19:31.720
Do you know why?

19:33.520 --> 19:34.520
I don't know,

19:34.720 --> 19:35.760
but I think

19:36.520 --> 19:38.320
he probably hates me.

19:38.840 --> 19:39.960
Thinking about it,

19:40.200 --> 19:43.040
he might regret rehearsing with me

19:43.560 --> 19:45.920
and lost confidence in me.

19:46.840 --> 19:49.400
Thinking it's better to give up

19:49.720 --> 19:51.880
than to lose face on stage.

19:52.880 --> 19:55.960
Otherwise, why didn't he answer

19:56.600 --> 19:58.400
after I called him so many times?

19:59.120 --> 20:00.240
Yuanbao.

20:01.120 --> 20:02.120
Actually,

20:02.720 --> 20:04.400
he could have just told me.

20:05.480 --> 20:08.280
If he told me, I would understand.

20:10.480 --> 20:13.200
Don't be sad suddenly.

20:13.640 --> 20:14.680
The doctor said

20:15.200 --> 20:16.560
you can't cry now.

20:18.280 --> 20:19.240
Listen to me,

20:19.840 --> 20:22.320
you are really, really excellent.

20:22.760 --> 20:24.960
You just haven't realized it yourself.

20:26.920 --> 20:29.560
Although I don't like Meng Jingu,

20:30.560 --> 20:33.000
and I'm also angry that he stood you up,

20:33.360 --> 20:34.440
but I don't think he would

20:34.440 --> 20:35.970
do something so classless.

20:37.560 --> 20:39.720
Maybe something really happened to him,

20:39.720 --> 20:41.520
so he couldn't answer your calls

20:41.560 --> 20:43.080
or make it to the competition.

20:43.080 --> 20:44.360
But the next day,

20:44.440 --> 20:46.170
he acted like nothing happened

20:46.320 --> 20:47.560
and went to school.

20:48.640 --> 20:49.880
Ruirui told me

20:50.040 --> 20:52.960
he didn't look like he had been through anything.

20:53.320 --> 20:55.240
Facing the gossiping from classmates,

20:55.240 --> 20:56.560
he didn't say a word.

20:56.760 --> 20:58.080
It was as if this

20:58.160 --> 20:59.680
never even happened.

21:01.880 --> 21:02.680
Don't worry.

21:03.160 --> 21:04.240
When I have time later,

21:04.240 --> 21:05.900
I'll go ask him what happened.

21:07.400 --> 21:08.040
How about this?

21:08.040 --> 21:09.640
Next time I see Meng Jingu,

21:09.920 --> 21:10.780
I'll beat him up

21:10.880 --> 21:12.040
to vent your anger.

21:12.840 --> 21:13.760
No.

21:15.360 --> 21:17.640
Why? Hearing I'm going to beat him up

21:17.720 --> 21:18.780
makes you feel bad?

21:18.880 --> 21:19.960
Not really.

21:20.240 --> 21:22.600
Since this is over,

21:22.920 --> 21:24.450
let's not mention it again.

21:24.840 --> 21:27.480
From now on, I'll just bother him less.

21:48.480 --> 21:49.960
Open your own homework.

21:52.880 --> 21:54.440
Look, there are actually many ways

21:54.440 --> 21:55.560
to solve this problem.

21:55.560 --> 21:57.020
The method you used before

21:57.280 --> 21:58.610
was quite complicated.

21:58.800 --> 22:00.120
I have a simpler way

22:00.160 --> 22:01.120
to solve it.

22:01.440 --> 22:02.560
Look, this...

22:06.880 --> 22:08.210
What are you looking at?

22:33.920 --> 22:35.960
How did you suddenly get so smart?

22:36.760 --> 22:38.560
Your physics grades are usually so bad.

22:38.560 --> 22:40.600
How did you suddenly get a flash of inspiration today

22:40.600 --> 22:41.860
and make so much sense?

22:45.200 --> 22:46.680
Well, I...

22:47.000 --> 22:49.240
I was afraid I wouldn't be able to explain it to you clearly,

22:49.240 --> 22:51.700
so I listened very carefully in class today.

22:53.320 --> 22:55.120
If you had been like this before,

22:55.200 --> 22:57.120
your grades would have improved long ago.

22:57.120 --> 22:59.920
You wouldn't have worse grades than me every time.

23:01.520 --> 23:02.520
I like it this way.

23:04.240 --> 23:06.100
I can't be bothered to talk to you.

23:25.040 --> 23:25.760
Yuanbao,

23:26.600 --> 23:27.840
how is your injury?

23:36.000 --> 23:37.760
Why haven't you gone back to rest?

23:37.760 --> 23:38.600
Jingu.

23:39.240 --> 23:41.600
When I went to find Yuanbao on the day of the competition,

23:41.600 --> 23:43.400
before I had time to explain to her,

23:43.400 --> 23:45.760
she was injured and sent to the hospital.

23:46.120 --> 23:47.240
Thank you, Xinrui.

23:47.600 --> 23:49.860
For making a special trip for me that day.

23:49.880 --> 23:51.160
I couldn't even help you.

23:51.160 --> 23:52.960
I already feel very bad about it.

23:53.800 --> 23:55.600
How about I find another time

23:55.840 --> 23:57.160
to help you explain to Yuanbao?

23:57.160 --> 23:57.880
No need.

23:58.160 --> 23:59.560
I'll find an opportunity

23:59.560 --> 24:01.090
to explain to her in person.

24:02.080 --> 24:02.880
Okay.

24:04.960 --> 24:07.960
Are you still mad at your dad?

24:10.200 --> 24:11.730
He's just too dictatorial.

24:12.000 --> 24:13.000
Since I was young,

24:13.440 --> 24:15.770
I've been controlled by him like a puppet.

24:16.120 --> 24:16.760
Forget it.

24:17.240 --> 24:18.700
Let's not talk about this.

24:18.880 --> 24:20.080
I can understand you.

24:20.240 --> 24:20.900
So just now,

24:20.920 --> 24:22.560
I talked to your parents for a long time.

24:22.560 --> 24:23.760
They have promised that

24:23.760 --> 24:25.360
as long as your grades remain stable,

24:25.360 --> 24:26.280
they will try their best to give you space

24:26.280 --> 24:27.480
and no longer interfere with your decisions.

24:27.480 --> 24:28.160
Really?

24:28.240 --> 24:28.960
Really.

24:29.360 --> 24:31.620
It's just that they are elders after all.

24:31.880 --> 24:34.880
They are too embarrassed to say some things in person,

24:35.080 --> 24:37.140
so they asked me to pass this on to you.

24:39.040 --> 24:41.100
Don't be mad at your parents anymore.

24:41.680 --> 24:43.480
They definitely mean well.

24:43.600 --> 24:46.660
It's just that their methods might not be appropriate.

24:47.000 --> 24:47.760
I know.

24:49.800 --> 24:50.400
By the way,

24:52.040 --> 24:54.200
you've been busy with the drama performance recently,

24:54.200 --> 24:56.200
I was too embarrassed to bother you.

24:57.240 --> 24:59.320
Now that this is finally over,

24:59.680 --> 25:01.240
can I ask you a favor?

25:01.640 --> 25:02.440
Tell me.

25:03.560 --> 25:05.760
As you know, I studied abroad for a year,

25:05.960 --> 25:07.480
and fell behind on a lot of domestic courses.

25:07.480 --> 25:09.010
You used to help me catch up.

25:09.200 --> 25:10.560
Could I trouble you

25:10.640 --> 25:12.240
to tutor me again in the future?

25:12.240 --> 25:13.040
Of course.

25:13.320 --> 25:14.000
Really?

25:14.280 --> 25:15.640
Then it's a promise.

25:18.280 --> 25:19.480
Signed and sealed.

25:22.080 --> 25:22.880
Also,

25:23.040 --> 25:25.100
your health is still very important.

25:25.320 --> 25:28.200
I've been busy lately and haven't had time to ask.

25:28.440 --> 25:29.770
How is your back injury?

25:30.800 --> 25:33.040
I was in a hurry to find Yuanbao that day,

25:33.400 --> 25:35.800
and accidentally fell again.

25:36.240 --> 25:38.840
What's wrong? Do you need to go to the hospital?

25:39.080 --> 25:40.340
Don't worry, I'm fine.

25:40.400 --> 25:41.240
I've applied some medicine,

25:41.240 --> 25:42.970
and it will be fine in a few days.

25:43.120 --> 25:44.240
I'm sorry, Xinrui.

25:45.520 --> 25:47.640
I was out of my mind with anger that day.

25:47.640 --> 25:49.320
Knowing you have a back injury,

25:49.320 --> 25:50.960
I still let you go to such a far place.

25:50.960 --> 25:51.440
I...

25:51.520 --> 25:53.240
Why are you being so polite to me?

25:53.240 --> 25:54.840
Besides, even if you didn't ask,

25:54.840 --> 25:57.440
I would still go to Yuanbao to explain clearly.

25:58.240 --> 25:59.080
Don't worry.

26:00.400 --> 26:01.640
Thank you, Xinrui.

26:02.240 --> 26:04.880
Alright, stop thanking me so much.

26:05.880 --> 26:07.000
Hurry up and drink your milk.

26:07.000 --> 26:08.060
I'll go back first.

26:09.640 --> 26:10.240
By the way.

26:11.160 --> 26:13.290
Shall we start tutoring this weekend?

26:15.600 --> 26:16.240
Bye.

26:50.920 --> 26:52.240
Auntie, Grandmother.

26:53.680 --> 26:54.840
I'm Yuanbao's desk mate.

26:54.840 --> 26:56.040
My name is Meng Jingu.

26:56.080 --> 26:57.520
I heard Yuanbao was injured.

26:57.520 --> 26:58.580
So I came to see her.

26:58.640 --> 26:59.960
So you are Meng Jingu.

27:00.240 --> 27:02.040
I've heard Yuanbao mention you.

27:02.160 --> 27:03.000
Oh, child.

27:03.160 --> 27:05.400
You shouldn't have brought so much fruit.

27:05.400 --> 27:05.920
Yes.

27:06.400 --> 27:08.680
Yuanbao, how are you feeling?

27:11.160 --> 27:12.480
I'm much better.

27:13.080 --> 27:16.280
Luckily, it was just a scrape on the eyelid.

27:17.560 --> 27:19.160
Come, sit on the sofa.

27:19.440 --> 27:20.360
Yes, come in.

27:20.400 --> 27:20.960
Come on.

27:21.000 --> 27:21.840
Thank you, Grandma. Thank you, Auntie.

27:21.840 --> 27:22.960
I'll cut some fruit for you.

27:22.960 --> 27:24.200
Sit here.

27:34.600 --> 27:36.440
How did you know my address?

27:36.680 --> 27:38.040
I asked Tong Ruirui.

27:40.840 --> 27:41.600
I see.

27:42.080 --> 27:43.210
I'm sorry, Yuanbao.

27:43.760 --> 27:44.560
That day,

27:45.360 --> 27:46.760
I didn't mean not to come.

27:48.480 --> 27:49.280
It's okay.

27:50.160 --> 27:52.720
It's fine. I know you're busy.

27:53.160 --> 27:54.120
It's okay.

27:54.840 --> 27:57.720
Good thing Mutou and Yaqi were there.

27:58.280 --> 28:00.360
As long as everything went smoothly.

28:00.560 --> 28:01.890
Actually, that day I...

28:02.120 --> 28:03.780
You're only apologizing now.

28:04.320 --> 28:05.580
Isn't it a bit too late?

28:07.120 --> 28:10.000
Yuanbao, I know no matter what I say,

28:10.080 --> 28:11.040
wrong is wrong.

28:12.080 --> 28:13.340
But please believe me,

28:13.520 --> 28:15.380
I didn't mean not to come that day,

28:15.920 --> 28:18.180
nor did I intentionally not contact you.

28:18.640 --> 28:19.800
Here.

28:20.200 --> 28:22.080
The fruit is cut. Have some.

28:22.200 --> 28:23.760
Come, Jingu, eat some fruit.

28:23.760 --> 28:24.820
Thank you, Auntie.

28:25.240 --> 28:26.370
Thank you, Grandma.

28:26.480 --> 28:27.440
Have you eaten?

28:27.880 --> 28:29.540
I came straight after school.

28:30.200 --> 28:31.320
Great.

28:31.760 --> 28:33.360
I cooked a lot of dishes today.

28:33.360 --> 28:34.360
Stay for dinner.

28:34.840 --> 28:36.720
Yes, try Grandma's cooking.

28:36.880 --> 28:38.080
No need.

28:43.360 --> 28:44.690
What do you mean no need?

28:44.840 --> 28:47.400
Jingu usually helps our Yuanbao a lot.

28:47.560 --> 28:49.440
And he even came especially to see Yuanbao today.

28:49.440 --> 28:50.840
You must stay for dinner.

28:51.120 --> 28:53.160
These two kids are so insensitive.

28:54.040 --> 28:55.960
Auntie, I really don't need to.

28:56.040 --> 28:56.760
Jingu,

28:57.320 --> 28:58.920
stay for dinner.

28:59.040 --> 29:00.500
Don't listen to those two.

29:00.680 --> 29:01.240
Let's go.

29:01.280 --> 29:02.440
Let's go cook.

29:11.840 --> 29:12.640
Jingu,

29:13.400 --> 29:16.000
I heard you're always first in your class.

29:16.400 --> 29:18.920
More than that. First in the whole grade.

29:20.640 --> 29:21.680
This kid,

29:21.840 --> 29:24.080
so good-looking and smart.

29:24.200 --> 29:25.280
Truly wonderful.

29:27.000 --> 29:27.920
Eat more.

29:28.560 --> 29:29.690
Thank you, Grandma.

29:30.080 --> 29:32.600
Qingyun, you should learn from him

29:32.760 --> 29:34.490
and get first place for Mom too.

29:35.480 --> 29:36.520
Okay, Mom.

29:37.080 --> 29:38.160
I heard from Yuanbao

29:38.160 --> 29:41.080
that you often help her with her homework at school.

29:41.440 --> 29:43.970
Yuanbao is my desk mate. It's what I should do.

29:45.080 --> 29:46.920
Such a loyal kid.

29:47.400 --> 29:48.240
Jingu,

29:48.680 --> 29:50.360
Auntie has a favor to ask.

29:50.760 --> 29:52.960
I don't know if it's convenient for you.

29:53.000 --> 29:53.840
Auntie.

29:54.040 --> 29:54.970
Tell me, Auntie.

29:55.600 --> 29:57.440
I'll try my best if I can do it.

29:58.920 --> 29:59.840
You see,

30:00.200 --> 30:02.320
your final exams are coming up soon.

30:03.000 --> 30:05.600
Yuanbao's grades weren't ideal to begin with.

30:05.680 --> 30:07.120
Now her eyes are injured,

30:07.200 --> 30:08.800
and she has fallen behind in her studies.

30:08.800 --> 30:10.600
If you have time on the weekends,

30:10.600 --> 30:11.840
could you come to our house

30:11.840 --> 30:13.480
and tutor our Yuanbao?

30:14.560 --> 30:15.400
Is that okay?

30:23.040 --> 30:24.720
Just forget it if it's too much trouble.

30:24.720 --> 30:26.120
Auntie was just asking.

30:26.200 --> 30:27.400
Don't overthink it.

30:30.120 --> 30:32.600
Auntie, no problem. I have time.

30:35.440 --> 30:36.520
That's great.

30:36.720 --> 30:37.480
Come on.

30:37.720 --> 30:39.400
Jingu, eat more.

30:43.920 --> 30:44.760
Thank you.

30:45.640 --> 30:49.440
Mom, I can also tutor Yuanbao.

30:49.600 --> 30:51.330
We don't need to bother others.

30:54.600 --> 30:55.600
Almost forgot.

30:57.240 --> 30:58.800
Since you're already tutoring one,

30:58.800 --> 31:00.320
you might as well tutor two.

31:00.320 --> 31:01.650
Take our Qingyun along,

31:01.800 --> 31:03.240
and tutor him too.

31:07.240 --> 31:07.920
Yeah.

31:10.160 --> 31:11.720
Mom, I don't need his tutoring.

31:11.720 --> 31:13.480
What do you mean you don't need it?

31:13.480 --> 31:16.080
Jingu hasn't even said if he wants to tutor you yet.

31:16.080 --> 31:17.280
Don't be ungrateful.

31:20.400 --> 31:22.040
Sure, Auntie. I can do it.

31:23.720 --> 31:24.200
That's great.

31:24.200 --> 31:25.480
Come on, eat up.

31:25.920 --> 31:27.720
You can set the time.

31:27.840 --> 31:29.360
Whenever you say you'll come,

31:29.360 --> 31:31.240
we'll start tutoring. Is that okay?

31:31.240 --> 31:32.370
No problem, Auntie.

31:34.120 --> 31:37.040
Okay, then I guess I have to thank you.

31:37.480 --> 31:39.040
Thank you, Meng.

31:39.760 --> 31:40.760
You're welcome.
